<div class="heading resPageHeading">


























<h1 >A history of making ourselves heard</h1></div>

<div class="content stackparsys">










				
				<div class="resImageText section">


























		<div class="row" id="23f60b4d-9e70-4c6d-9c38-83efc392e82e">
			<div class="col-xs-12">
				<div class="thumbnail customStyle1">
					
<img src="/content/dam/research/images/newsletter/2020-07/making-ourselves-heard-0.jpg" alt="A stack of old black-and-white advertisements for electronics"/>




					 
						<div class="caption richtextContent">
	<p>At the heart of professor Art Blake’s recent research was an exploration of citizens band (CB) radio, a communications technology launched in the United States in 1948 which steadily grew in popularity over the next two decades.</p>
</div>
						    
					
